<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 12:21:56 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>所罗门群岛议员周四投票选出新总理，因中国交易着眼</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/solomon-islands-lawmakers-vote-thursday-new-pm-china-deals-eyed-2024-05-01/</link><description>所罗门群岛立法者将于周四在外交部长耶利米·马内莱和反对派领袖马修·韦尔之间进行无记名投票，选出新总理，此前全国选举未能让任何政党获得多数席位。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 12:09:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/solomon-islands-lawmakers-vote-thursday-new-pm-china-deals-eyed-2024-05-01/</guid></item><item><title>中国和美国需求放缓给星巴克前景蒙上阴影，星巴克股价暴跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/starbucks-shares-tumble-china-us-demand-slowdown-clouds-outlook-2024-05-01/</link><description>星巴克股价周三收盘前下跌近 14%，此前这家咖啡连锁店因美国消费者对通胀的疲软需求持续疲软以及中国经济复苏慢于预期而下调了年度预期。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 12:06:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/starbucks-shares-tumble-china-us-demand-slowdown-clouds-outlook-2024-05-01/</guid></item><item><title>雅诗兰黛因美国和中国需求复苏而上调年度利润预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/estee-lauder-lifts-annual-profit-view-us-china-demand-recovery-2024-05-01/</link><description>随着美国和亚太市场对 MAC 口红制造商高价护肤品和香水的需求反弹，雅诗兰黛周三上调了年度利润预期，第三季度业绩超出了华尔街的目标。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 10:49:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/estee-lauder-lifts-annual-profit-view-us-china-demand-recovery-2024-05-01/</guid></item><item><title>由于投资者等待 iPhone 中的人工智能，苹果销量将大幅下滑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-set-big-sales-decline-investors-await-ai-iphones-2024-05-01/</link><description>苹果计划在其 iPhone 中添加生成式人工智能并重振在关键的中国市场的疲软销售，这将成为周四的焦点，预计这家科技巨头将公布一年多以来最大的季度收入跌幅。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 10:38:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-set-big-sales-decline-investors-await-ai-iphones-2024-05-01/</guid></item><item><title>路透社/益普索调查发现，大多数美国人将 TikTok 视为中国的影响力工具</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/most-americans-see-tiktok-chinese-influence-tool-reutersipsos-poll-finds-2024-05-01/</link><description>路透社/益普索 (Ipsos) 进行的一项民意调查显示，大多数美国人认为，中国利用 TikTok 来塑造美国公众舆论，而华盛顿距离可能禁止这款中国短视频应用程序又近了一步。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 10:12:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/most-americans-see-tiktok-chinese-influence-tool-reutersipsos-poll-finds-2024-05-01/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：随着美联储 2024 年降息希望渺茫，债券迎来五一节</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-05-01/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 10:05:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-05-01/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，印度不太可能对低品位铁矿石实施出口限制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-unlikely-impose-export-curbs-low-grade-iron-ore-source-says-2024-05-01/</link><description>一位直接了解情况的消息人士称，尽管印度对中国的海外销售不断增加，但印度目前不太可能对低品位铁矿石出口征收关税，并拒绝了小型钢铁生产商的要求。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 09:22:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-unlikely-impose-export-curbs-low-grade-iron-ore-source-says-2024-05-01/</guid></item><item><title>美联储政策决定前美元接近五个月高点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-01/</link><description>美元兑一篮子货币小幅升至今年最高水平，周三美国股指期货在美联储政策决定之前下跌，但由于许多欧洲和亚洲市场休市，交投清淡。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 08:46:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-01/</guid></item><item><title>壳牌退出中国电力市场业务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/shell-exits-china-power-market-businesses-2024-05-01/</link><description>壳牌已退出中国电力市场，这是其首席执行官瓦尔·萨万 (Wael Sawan) 致力于专注于利润更高的业务（包括天然气和石油业务）的一部分。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 08:37:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/shell-exits-china-power-market-businesses-2024-05-01/</guid></item><item><title>华为备受瞩目的消费者首席执行官余承东转变角色</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/huaweis-high-profile-consumer-boss-richard-yu-shifts-role-2024-05-01/</link><description>两位知情人士表示，中国华为技术有限公司 (HWT.UL) 已将备受瞩目的消费者业务负责人余承东调任该部门董事长。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 06:39:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/huaweis-high-profile-consumer-boss-richard-yu-shifts-role-2024-05-01/</guid></item><item><title>中国启动下一代航母海试</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-launches-sea-trials-next-generation-aircraft-carrier-2024-05-01/</link><description>据官方媒体报道，中国周三为第三艘也是最先进的航母福建舰进行了海试。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 02:44:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-launches-sea-trials-next-generation-aircraft-carrier-2024-05-01/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾称中国海警加剧南海紧张局势</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-chinese-coast-guard-elevating-tensions-south-china-sea-2024-05-01/</link><description>一名官员表示，在北京使用水炮造成两艘船只受损后，菲律宾周三指责中国海警加剧南海紧张局势。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 02:40:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-chinese-coast-guard-elevating-tensions-south-china-sea-2024-05-01/</guid></item><item><title>台湾对中国就职后的演习保持警惕</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-alert-post-inauguration-chinese-drills-2024-05-01/</link><description>台湾最高安全官员周三表示，在当选总统赖清德本月就职后，台湾对中国进行军事演习保持警惕，并补充说中国已经开始使用不寻常的新策略。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 02:34:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-alert-post-inauguration-chinese-drills-2024-05-01/</guid></item><item><title>由于美国和中国主要市场需求降温，星巴克下调年度销售预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/starbucks-reports-surprise-fall-quarterly-sales-2024-04-30/</link><description>星巴克周二下调了年度销售预期，此前该公司报告同店销售额近三年来首次下降，原因是该公司面临美国和中国这两个最大市场的咖啡需求疲软的困境。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 20:10:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/starbucks-reports-surprise-fall-quarterly-sales-2024-04-30/</guid></item><item><title>美国劳工官员呼吁企业退出中国新疆</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/us-labor-official-calls-companies-exit-chinas-xinjiang-2024-04-30/</link><description>美国劳工部官员周二表示，出于对强迫劳动的担忧，国际公司无法在新疆负责任地运营，应该离开中国西部地区。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 17:46:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/us-labor-official-calls-companies-exit-chinas-xinjiang-2024-04-30/</guid></item></channel></rss>